==English==

===Etymology===
Prefix ''a-'' + ''beam''.

===Adjective===
'''abeam'''

# {{nautical}} On the [[beam]], that is, on a [[line]] which forms a right angle with the [[ship's]] [[keel]]; opposite to the center of the ship's side.
# {{nautical}} [[direction|Direction]]al term meaning at a [[right angle]] to the [[centerline]] or [[keel]] of a [[vessel]]. (FM 55-501).

